improved_metadata.title: Spray Foam Blues
improved_metadata.description: A humorous song about the struggles and frustrations of working with spray foam insulation, dealing with clogged tips and faulty equipment. It captures the exasperation and near-quitting point of a tradesperson.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: My tip didn't come in, it just ain't fun to hold but it
